# Snapshot of gbrain skill-pack dir names, so gbrain:<name> refs are CI-gated
# deterministically (CI checkouts have no gbrain pack). lint-refs-resolve.py
# resolves gbrain:* tokens against THIS list everywhere; when the local pack is
# present it also freshness-checks every entry against the real dirs.
# Regenerate: (cd ~/site/knowledge/brain/skills && ls -d */ | grep -v '^_' | tr -d /)
brain-ops
brain-pdf
briefing
conventions
cron-scheduler
cross-modal-review
enrich
ingest
maintain
query
repo-architecture
reports
skill-creator
skillify
skillpack-check
testing
